{"title":"京剧现代戏人物赞","authors":["叶浅予　袁鹰"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":6,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"京剧现代戏人物赞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《黛婼》〔云南京剧院演出〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶浅予　画　袁　鹰　诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光清露来滋养，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜看新苗长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻身孤女显英姿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记得鞭痕泪影少年时。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青山铺起黄金路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕风和雨？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云消雾散好家园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长是春光万里艳阳天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}